    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i'm still a bit worried though. it's not just tingly, it feels like i can't really grip things well with my left hand and the numbness is spreading a bit up my shoulder. but u seem pretty sure it's just the flight. r u sure i don't need to go to a clinic or something? i don't want to make a big deal out of nothing if it's just fatigue.",
